cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SI, cs.DC 

This paper primarily focuses on security risks in the npm ecosystem, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses issues related to software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), system and information theory (cs.SI), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) as they relate to the npm ecosystem.
